=3D"116:1-116:107;6515-6621">Rule 1 =E2=80=94 <code class=3D"bg-text-200/5 =
border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rou=
nded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">st.session_state</code> is the only=
 persistence mechanism; local variables are rebuilt every rerun</h3>

<p class=3D"font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal" data-s=
ourcepos=3D"118:1-121:49;6623-6944">Every variable prefixed <code class=3D"=
